    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the reassurance. i was worried it might be an infection but it sounds like it's just part of the healing then. do you think i should use a specific brand of antibiotic cream? also, how often should i be doing the warm compress? i don't want to overdo it and irritate the skin more if it's already sensitive.",
